source:
TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var> Quest Sync<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
Viraban is wringing her hands nervously.
target:
TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>特殊ルール： レベルアジャスト<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
パーラカの里にいるヴィラバンは、落ち込んでいるようだ。

source: TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_TODO_00<tab>Retrieve the worn charm from a hanuman langur.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_TODO_00<tab><var 28 ((BNpcName)) F229D401 /var>を討伐し、まれに得られる<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E910E01 /var>を入手

source: TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the worn charm to Viraban.
TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_000<tab>Egads, my knees... My years are catching up to me...
target:
TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_000<tab>いたた……。
もう歳なのかしら、いやになるねぇ。

source: TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_001<tab>You there, traveler, might you have some time to spare for an old maid? As I fled from the chaos that erupted, I took a terrible spill and dropped a charm that is very important to me.
target:
TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_001<tab>ああ、旅の方、聞いておくれよ。
終末の騒ぎで森へ逃げたとき、派手に転んでねぇ。
膝を痛めたうえに、大切な御守を落としてしまったんだよ。

source: TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_002<tab>And can you believe it? One of those flea-infested hanuman langurs scooped it up off the ground and scurried off into the woods.
target:
TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_002<tab>しかも、光り物に目がない<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F229D401 /var>が、
あっという間に、その御守を持ち去ってしまって！
情けないかぎりだよ……。

source: TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_003<tab>Would that I still had my youth─I'd skewer that fiend at the end of my spear! Alas, my vigor isn't what it once was, and I'm still aching from that fall besides...
target:
TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_003<tab>若い頃は、神獣様を祀る遺跡を護る守護者として、
森の動物たちを相手に槍を振るっていたってのに。
まったく、歳はとりたくないもんだねぇ……。

source: TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_A1_000_001<tab>You'll have your charm back, don't worry.
TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_A1_000_002<tab>You should get your wounds treated first.
target: TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_A1_000_002<tab>今は怪我を治すことに専念して

source: TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_006<tab>If I wait for my wounds to heal, who knows where that monster will get to. I must have that charm back. Please, will you lend me your stout arm?
target:
TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_006<tab>年寄りは、怪我の治りも遅くなるしねぇ……。
この足では取り戻すことも難しそうだし、
もしよければ、あなたの手を貸してもらえないかい？

source: TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_007<tab>The animal ran off toward the Font of Maya. Fell it quickly and return my charm to me, please. How else am I to defend myself from fate's cruel machinations?
target:
TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_007<tab>マーヤーの幻泉に住まう「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F229D401 /var>」を倒して、
「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E910E01 /var>」を見つけたら、届けてほしいの。
気が向いたときでいいから、お願いねぇ。

source: TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_008<tab>Go to the Font of Maya and retrieve my charm. Please be quick─I can already feel my luck souring.
target:
TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_008<tab>マーヤーの幻泉に住まう「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F229D401 /var>」を倒して、
「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E910E01 /var>」を見つけたら、届けてほしいの。
気が向いたときでいいから、お願いねぇ。

source: TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_010<tab>You are returned at last, and none too soon─I feel that something terrible is soon to happen. Were you able to slay that monster?
target:
TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_010<tab>まあまあ、旅の方。
また声をかけてくれて嬉しいよ。
……おや、手に持っているそれは……。

source: TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_011<tab>Yes, this is it! This is it! I can already feel my vitality returning, such as it is. Death shall have to wait for many years yet! Thank you, traveler.
target:
TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_011<tab>ああ、これはまさしく「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E910E01 /var>」！
取り返してくれて、本当にありがとう……。

source: TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_012<tab>I received this charm in my youth, when I was handed my spear and deemed a warrior true. It was passed down through our order, and I keep it still to remember my halcyon days.
target:
TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_012<tab>この御守はね、私が守護者として一人前になったとき、
先達から贈ってもらった、大切な品なのよ。

source: TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_013<tab>Although my fighting days are long behind me, I would be happy to impart some small measure of my knowledge to the stewards of the future. In time, I shall give this charm away, just as it was given to me.
target:
TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_013<tab>今は老いて、戦えなくなってたけれど、
先達のように、後進を育てることはできるかしら。
守護者の務めを引き継ぐ若者へ、この御守を託す頃合かねぇ。

source: TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_014<tab>When I relinquish it, I shall tell its recipient of your bravery this day, that your deeds might echo into the future. Please, take this as a reward. It's the least I can give.
target:
TEXT_AKTKZF001_04256_VIRABAN_000_014<tab>御守を受け継ぐときには、
恩人であるあなたのことも伝えておくよ。
世話になったねぇ、お礼にこれを受け取っておくれ。
